_:Bbf7454755fb55c40221d120da5e8e525 <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#annotatedTarget> "A non-striated muscle that is composed of spindle-shaped cells. Smooth muscle usually is organized into sheets that line cavitated organs.[TAO]" <https://purl.wholepersonphysiome.org/wpp/muscular-system> .
